rows.label: qst200801_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey, everyone. Don't you think
this Saffronia tree is wonderful?

rows.label: qst200801_msg0004
rows.name: Do you have some business with us?

rows.label: qst200801_msg0007
rows.name: Hand over the classified documents now!

rows.label: qst200801_msg0008
rows.name:
Huh? What are you talking
about? I don't know...

rows.label: qst200801_msg0010
rows.name:
We've already confirmed
that you have them!

rows.label: qst200801_msg0011
rows.name:
Even if you say that, I don't
know what I don't know...

rows.label: qst200801_msg0012
rows.name: Hotaru, do you really not know?

rows.label: qst200801_msg0014
rows.name: He says. Isn't it a misunderstanding?

rows.label: qst200801_msg0015
rows.name:
Hah! So you're going to
play dumb to the end...

rows.label: qst200801_msg0016
rows.name:
If you're not going to return them,
we'll just take them by force!

rows.label: qst200801_msg0018
rows.name:
Shut up! It's because
you won't return them!

rows.label: qst200801_msg0019
rows.name:
Don't regret it if you
get seriously injured!!
